OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1773486371
OL,3,CFilm studio and arena set to benefit
OL,4,Cfrom #104m funding boost
OL,6,FA #104million package aimed at
OL,7,Fboosting the North East's creative
OL,8,Findustries has been announced.
OL,10,FPart of the investment will help to
OL,11,Fbuild and open the Crown Works film
OL,12,Fstudios in Sunderland, which would be
OL,13,Fone of the largest in the North of
OL,14,FEngland when it opens in 2027.
OL,16,FConstruction on the project on the
OL,17,Fbanks of the River Wear is meant to
OL,18,Fstart in July.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
