CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1773486371
OL,3,CFilm studio and arena set to benefit
OL,4,Cfrom #104m funding boost
OL,6,FThere will also be #24m of funding for
OL,7,FGateshead Quays, a proposed 12,500-
OL,8,F15,000 seat arena, as well as for
OL,9,Fsmall venues and a festivals programme.
OL,11,FNorth East Mayor Kim McGuinness, who
OL,12,Fannounced the funding package today,
OL,13,Fsaid: "We've heard leading voices from
OL,14,FSam Fender to Jade talk about their
OL,15,Fpride in their North East roots and
OL,16,Fthe huge barriers working class young
OL,17,Fpeople from the north face when trying
OL,18,Fto make it in music and film.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1773486371
OL,3,CFilm studio and arena set to benefit
OL,4,Cfrom #104m funding boost
OL,6,F"I said in my manifesto I'd change
OL,7,Fthat, and here's the next big step -
OL,8,F#104m backing both the inspirational
OL,9,Fbig venues to the vital local space
OL,10,Fneed for your first gig. Last week we
OL,11,Fannounced the skills funding to help
OL,12,Fyou learn on the job, this week we're
OL,13,Fbacking more venues.
OL,15,F"If you have a creative dream, you
OL,16,Fdon't need London to succeed. We'll
OL,17,Fprove that."
OL,19,FThe package of investments is set to
OL,20,Fbe considered by the North East
OL,21,FCombined Authority Cabinet next week.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
