PN,42904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1773486371
OL,3,CFilm studio and arena set to benefit
OL,4,Cfrom #104m funding boost
OL,6,FThe meeting will hear that the
OL,7,Fcreative industries is among the
OL,8,Ffastest growing sectors in the UK,
OL,9,Fwith the North East outperforming all
OL,10,Fother English regions in recent years.
OL,12,FThe investment marks the first major
OL,13,Fscheme since the Newcastle-Gateshead
OL,14,FMayoral Development Zone was created
OL,15,Flast year.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/5
